{"type": "article", "id": 12807, "title": "1964 年日本奥运主场馆拆除再利用", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-30T07:50:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061405208wTVfdC4qr6X1kjp.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本最近为了为 2020 年的奥运主办挪地方，决定拆除 1964 年的奥运主场馆，在原址上建一个新的竞技场。但他们没有把废旧的物品全部摧毁，而是回收了场馆内的蓝色坐垫，找来了三组新锐设计师，与日本木家具厂商 KARIMOKU 合作，一起推出了三款椅子，把蓝色坐垫重新利用，不仅珍藏多年前的记忆，同时也起到了宣传的作用。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140523gOLj96vSemCkcMZo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140523QrcCPDS1UkizEF9s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140523ArZyIuxURPG2nvaK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140524gEhL8uCIjmS7wQep.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6453125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140524VeuZW7hfM2P069b1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140525EmzpDRcWTv54yUwV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140525XfUY7E3Z6W0qAht1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140525dgBsFoS7jnhXaUrP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261405263hFIP8SYMevKdVbX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140526Hu13U97jIEpWnaRw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}